    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108190/extras/438793bced9604519924fcd1b31db075.poster.avif?t=1768532776\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108190/extras/438793bced9604519924fcd1b31db075.webm?t=1768532776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108190/extras/feab16b034a8848afa78083d8757624c.poster.avif?t=1768532776\" width=640 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108190/extras/feab16b034a8848afa78083d8757624c.webm?t=1768532776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle Depot is a retro-inspired sokoban game, featuring fun characters, vast environments, and a robust level editor. Journey through a post-apocalyptic world, solving puzzles with a staggering number of mechanics and object interactions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Union Freight Operations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What starts as a simple matter of pushing boxes around a warehouse quickly escalates into a perilous puzzle adventure through a world of giant insects and rogue robots. Survive deadly roach-filled grottos, bubbling lakes of caustic goop, and the twisted industrial ruins of the eponymous Depot-13. Join survivors Stella, Todd, and other memorable characters in this comedic retro-futuristic brain-expanding quest through the most puzzling of Depots! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you prepared for an exciting career in the field of cargo management?  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A classic pixel-art aesthetic and bumpin' soundtrack brings the world of Puzzle Depot to life!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each sprawling level is jam-packed with puzzling rooms, optional goals, and secrets to find.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploit dangerous fauna to help solve puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect useful tools to improve your puzzle solving capabilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Undo moves, restart rooms, replay levels, and save your game anywhere you like. Convenient!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as several characters with unique abilities for tackling the Depot's many challenges. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover deep lore and bad jokes through various notes, datalogs, and dialogue.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create and share your own nefarious puzzles with a fully-featured level editor!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100% created by real-life human beings!</p></li></ul>",
